iaik.pdf.asn1objects

Class OtherRevInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • iaik.pdf.asn1objects.OtherRevInfo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    iaik.asn1.ASN1Type

    public class OtherRevInfo
extends java.lang.Object
implements iaik.asn1.ASN1Type
    This class represents the ASN.1 structure OtherRevInfo as defined in PDF specification ISO 32000-1. This structure can be used as component of the RevocationInfoArchival structure, to specify other revocation information than OCSP and CRL. 
     OtherRevInfo ::= SEQUENCE {
                Type OBJECT IDENTIFIER
                Value OCTET STRING
 }
